Even the daughter with the down payment deserves it.

13
00:00:15.733 --> 00:00:17.933
Look, you have been married to our Gu family for so many years

14
00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:19.200
It's the same thing.

15
00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:20.333
