21
00:00:30.766 --> 00:00:31.333
I'll tell you what.

22
00:00:31.333 --> 00:00:31.933
You and my son

23
00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:33.400
Not from the same world at all

24
00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:35.000
