25
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:36.683
Hurry up and sign these administrative letters

26
00:00:36.683 --> 00:00:37.783
Get out of the house

27
00:00:39.966 --> 00:00:41.683
Mom, this is what you mean.

28
00:00:41.683 --> 00:00:42.566
I don't believe it.

29
00:00:42.566 --> 00:00:44.250
