33
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:50.933
What's the noise?

34
00:00:52.850 --> 00:00:54.200
Dean, come here

35
00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:55.733
Explain it to mom

36
00:00:55.733 --> 00:00:57.433
