37
00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:00.183
I was going to give you some toughness

38
00:01:00.483 --> 00:01:02.200
I never thought you were so shameless

39
00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:03.483
Since you want to ask me

40
00:01:03.483 --> 00:01:05.150
